  content: 'The 5 benefits now compound with AI assistance. <strong>GitHub Copilot for Pull Requests</strong> auto-generates code review comments. <strong>CodiumAI / Codium PR Agent</strong> writes test cases + suggests refactors. <strong>Cursor + Continue.dev</strong> let you ask an LLM "review this for bugs" inline. Limitation: AI catches obvious issues but misses business-logic defects — humans still essential for "does this match what the user actually wants?"'
